invalid type: string "passage: # 34 • Aviva\n\n**Security**  \n- All outside doors should have manufacturer-approved key locks.  \n- Fit locks to patio doors to prevent lifting off tracks.  \n- Ensure all windows, including skylights, are closed and fastened.  \n- Install security lighting at front, back, and sides, activated by movement or darkness.  \nnot include:  \nP5.\n\n# 2 • Aviva\n\n: 